2006-08-02 10:30 UTC-0300 Eduardo Fernandes <modalsist@yahoo.com.br>
  * source\rtl\dbedit.prg
    ! fixed run time error at codeblock argument verification.

  * source\rtl\ttxtlin.prg
    ! cleaned the code from my old changes to treat tab key. This one is not
      necessary anymore. Removed my old comments for that.

  * source\rtl\memoedit.prg
    + added full navigation of cursor into all lines and all columns into text
      in any direction.
    + added vertical scroll behaviour in reply to ME_TOGGLESCROLL from udf.
    + added aConfigurablekeys, aUnhandledkeys, aEditkeys, aMouseKeys, aAsciiKeys datas
    + created method ExistUdf.
    ! changed name of method xDo to CallUdf to better knowledgement.
    ! changed name of method HandleUserkey to HandleUdf.
    ! fixed treatment of exit with ESC if scoreboard is on. Only exit if user
      answer yes. Esc or No go back to edit text.
    ! fixed treatment of udf call to prevent infinite loop in any circustancies.
    ! fixed double call to Idlehook() method when ME_IDLE mode is detected.
    ! fixed double call to udf when udf is present and an key exception occurs.
    ! fixed old bug that was causing infinite loop when:
      Edit() -> KeyboardHook() -> HandleUserKey() -> Edit()
    ! fixed old bug in udf treatment that in any circunstancies cause infinite
      loop.
    ! clean code.
    - removed Idlehook method.
    

  * source\rtl\teditor.prg
    + added DelTextRight() method to delete from cursor to end of line.
    + added DelWordRight() method in response from CTRL-T key.
    + added DisplayInsert() method to diplay <insert> label at scoreboard
      area when insert is on.
    + added bKeyBlock data to treat setkey() in udf existence.
    + added LastRow() method do replace ::naTexlen data.
    + added GetCol() method to internal use.
    + added IsEmptyLine() method to internal use.
    ! changed lDirty data name to lChanged for better knowledge.
    ! fixed worwrapcol point to allow edit same amount of chars per line as
      Clipper memoedit.
    ! fixed delete method to remove a line when this line is empty.
    ! fixed wordright and wordleft to navigate from cursor upto begin/end of
      memo and vice-versa when lWordWrap is on.
    ! fixed backspace method to allow continue at end of previous line if
      lWordWrap is on.
    ! fixed return method in insert mode.
    ! fixed K_AScii to respect ::lWordWrap if it is on.
    ! fixed pagedown(), pageup(), down(), up(), left(), right(), wordright(),
      wordleft() methods to cursor freedom of movement.
    - removed code that call Setkey() in Edit() method to avoid double callÿ
      from memoedit.
    ! clean code.

    Note: 1) CTRL-END still doesn't work in separate mode of CTRL-W.
          2) At startup memoedit always will split text, even if lwordwrap
             is set to .f. at initialization mode. This behaviour need adjusts.

    I hope these changes fix some old bugs of memoedit. If no, I can revert
    all.

